description: Meski Healthy 2 Go is a delicious Ethiopian food truck serving the DC Streets with a mission to help customers gain access to simple, fresh, and delectable food. In American society today, a vast majority of our food is genetically modified and artificial, but this business hopes to change that. Meski provides a plethora of healthy options to choose from. This food speaks for itself.
name: Meski Healthy 2 Go
